                        <div class="row dnnpane">
                            <div id="dnn_FourGrid8" class="four_grid8 col-sm-8">
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8111"><a name="8111"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8111">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8111_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What is the difference between each service?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8111" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8111_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8111 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8111_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8111_HtmlModule_lblContent"
                                                                 class="Normal normalCheckBox">
                                                                <p><span class="anchor" id="services-descriptions"><!--anchor howorder--> </span>
                                                                </p>

                                                                <h3>A) Letter of Invitation</h3>

                                                                <p>Our basic visa service. We will provide you with a
                                                                    Letter of Invitation only so that you can prepare
                                                                    your application pack and apply at the visa
                                                                    application centre yourself. This the best option if
                                                                    you wish to handle your own application and keep
                                                                    costs to a minimum.</p>

                                                                <h3>B) Check and Prepare</h3>

                                                                <p>Our standard visa service. Before you apply for your
                                                                    visa yourself, we will check your documents to
                                                                    ensure they meet consulate requirements. We can also
                                                                    prepare your complete application pack for an
                                                                    additional fee. This is the best option if you are
                                                                    after flexibility in terms of cost and control of
                                                                    your application, but also want that added
                                                                    reassurance that your visa application is
                                                                    correct.</p>

                                                                <h3>C) Managed Visa Service</h3>

                                                                <p>Our premium visa service. We will provide you with a
                                                                    simple application form to fill in which we will use
                                                                    to complete the rest of the visa application process
                                                                    for you. This is the best option if you do not want
                                                                    the hassle of putting together your own visa
                                                                    application.</p>

                                                                <p><strong>Please note: Our Managed Visa Service is
                                                                        currently unavailable</strong></p>

                                                                <hr/>
                                                                <p>That&rsquo;s it ... we do the rest and you relax! One
                                                                    last thing though, to make sure we have got all the
                                                                    paperwork to successfully submit your visa
                                                                    application pack to the consulate, please take a
                                                                    look at the &ldquo; <a href="#docsrequired">documents
                                                                        required</a>&rdquo; section below and also
                                                                    confirm that the <a href="#proctimes">processing
                                                                        times</a> meet your travel needs.</p>

                                                                <ul class="arrow">
                                                                    <li><a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Group">Click here if you
                                                                            have a group of 4 or more for our group
                                                                            discount page</a></li>
                                                                    <li><a href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Calculator">Not sure
                                                                            which visa or service you need? Click here
                                                                            for our visa calculator</a></li>
                                                                </ul>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8111 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8112"><a name="8112"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
