                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8112_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p class="MsoNormal">Travellers need to provide a
                                                                    medical certificate to confirm they have tested
                                                                    negative for Covid-19 within 72 hours of arrival in
                                                                    Russia. We are now offering affordable PCR-
                                                                    certified COVID test kits to accompany our visa
