                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8113"><a name="8113"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8113">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8113_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What is a Russian Tourist Visa and is it right for me?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8113" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8113_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8113 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8113_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8113_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>A Russian tourist visa is an official document
                                                                    required when travelling to Russia for tourism,
                                                                    leisure or short business trips. They allow for
                                                                    either a single or double visit and are valid for a
                                                                    maximum period of 30 days.</p>
                                                                <p>The tourist visa will be issued for the exact dates
                                                                    you request, or as specified on the invitation if
                                                                    you are providing this yourself.</p>
                                                                <p>This is the most cost effective visa for short trips
                                                                    and if you know when and where you will be going,
                                                                    otherwise consider a <a
                                                                            href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Business">Russian
                                                                        Business visa</a>.</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8113 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
