                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8115_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8115 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8115_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8115_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>Prices start from &pound;144.23 for UK passport
                                                                    holders, though the final price will depend on your
                                                                    nationality, the number of visits you wish to make,
                                                                    how quickly you need your visa (service level) and
                                                                    any return delivery or postage. To see the exact
