                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8117"><a name="8117"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8117">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8117_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What documents do I need to provide with my application pack?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8117" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8117_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8117 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8117_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8117_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p><span class="anchor" id="docsrequired">
        <!--anchor docsrequired -->
    </span></p>
                                                                <p>The documents that you need to provide to allow us to
                                                                    lodge your application at the consulate depend on
                                                                    your
                                                                    nationality and residency in the United Kingdom.</p>
                                                                <p>Check your visa application requirements by selecting
                                                                    your passport nationality from the menu:</p>
                                                                <div id="nationalitySelect2Holder"
                                                                     class="form-group form-inline">
                                                                    <select class="nationalitySelectDD form-control">
                                                                        <option value="">Please select</option>
                                                                        <option value="United Kingdom">United Kingdom
                                                                        </option>
                                                                        <option value=""></option>
                                                                        [Visas:AllCountriesOptions]
                                                                    </select>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="grey_background">
                                                                    <div class="visas-documents-section"
                                                                         id="nationalityRequirements"></div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <p></p>
                                                            </div>


