                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8118"><a name="8118"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8118">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8118_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">When can I apply for my Russian tourist visa?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8118" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8118_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8118 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8118_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8118_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>Russian tourist visas are restricted to applying a
                                                                    maximum of six months in advance of the first entry
                                                                    date requested. This means that the Russian
                                                                    consulate is currently accepting tourist visa
                                                                    applications with a requested entry date that is on
                                                                    or before: 09 April 2022.</p>
                                                                <p>Please note that the consulate may vary the date that
                                                                    it accepts applications for operational reasons; and
                                                                    in this case we will contact you.</p>
                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8118 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8119"><a name="8119"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8119">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8119_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">How long can I stay in Russia using my visa?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8119" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8119_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8119 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8119_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8119_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p>A Russian tourist visa will be valid only for the
                                                                    exact dates you request when submitting your order
                                                                    online, or, if you are providing your own invitation
                                                                    it will be valid only for the dates listed on
                                                                    this.</p>

                                                                <p>Once you have your visa, you may enter Russia anytime
                                                                    after midnight of the validity start date and stay
                                                                    up to midnight of the validity end date.</p>

                                                                <p>It is important to note that:</p>

                                                                <ul>
                                                                    <li>a Russian tourist visa may be valid only for a
                                                                        maximum period of 30 days
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>you must never attempt to enter or leave Russia
                                                                        outside of the visa validity period detailed on
                                                                        the visa
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li>you may not use the visa once you have used the
                                                                        maximum number of entries and exits it allows;
                                                                        once for single entry visas and twice for double
                                                                        entry visas.
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ul>
                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8119 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8120"><a name="8120"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8120">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8120_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">What is the processing time?</span>
                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8120" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                <div class="panel-body">
                                                    <div id="dnn_ctr8120_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_8120 -->
                                                        <div id="dnn_ctr8120_ModuleContent"
                                                             class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                                                            <div id="dnn_ctr8120_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
                                                                <p><span class="anchor" id="proctimes"><!-- proctimes --></span>
                                                                </p>

                                                                <p>The processing time is the number of working days
                                                                    that it will take us to obtain your visa once we
                                                                    have received your documents and lodged your
                                                                    application with the Russian consulate. We will
                                                                    lodge your application the next consular working day
                                                                    after we receive it, provided all the documents are
                                                                    in order and you are able to visit the Russian Visa
                                                                    Application Centre to give your biometric data
                                                                    (fingerprints) &ndash; please <a
                                                                            href="https://realrussia.co.uk/Visas/Russian/Biometric">click
                                                                        here</a> for more information. Visa applications
                                                                    received by our office after 15.30 on weekdays or at
                                                                    any time on Saturdays or non-working days will not
                                                                    start to be processed by our staff until the
                                                                    following working day.</p>

                                                                <p>The visa due dates indicated on the order form
                                                                    account for UK and Russian public holidays however
                                                                    please note that the Russian consulate may
                                                                    experience delays when issuing the visas usually
                                                                    shortly after their holiday period is over. For that
                                                                    reason, the visa due dates are only provisional and
                                                                    by no means definitive. In any event, we do not
                                                                    recommend booking your flight or make other travel
                                                                    arrangements until you have got your passport and
                                                                    visa with you.</p>

                                                                <p>Please note: if you are travelling to the North
                                                                    Caucasus area (including but not restricted to
                                                                    Vladikavkaz, Magas, Machatschkala, Pyatigorsk) it
                                                                    will take the consulate 21 working days to process
                                                                    your visa, including those requested as &ldquo;Next
                                                                    Day&rdquo; services.</p>

                                                                <p>Depending upon your chosen method of delivery, we
                                                                    will either dispatch your passport to you on the day
                                                                    the visa is ready or hold it in our office for
                                                                    collection. For Royal Mail Special Delivery, this
                                                                    means that you will have your passport and visa the
                                                                    next business day.&rdquo;</p>

                                                                <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                                            </div>


                                                        </div><!-- End_Module_8120 --></div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-8121"><a name="8121"></a>

                                    <div class="panel-group rr-margined-block">
                                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                                <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                    <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapsible-8121">
                                                        <span id="dnn_ctr8121_dnnTITLE_titleLabel" class="Head">I am travelling on the Trans Mongolian, can you help me with these visas as well?</span>


                                                    </a>
                                                </h3>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="collapsible-8121" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
